DTEND:20260514T003000Z
DTSTAMP:20260513T063930Z
UID:311d679d-3c59-5566-803d-c77128fe3ed2
DESCRIPTION:Join your fellow Cycle Toronto members in this virtual town ha
 ll to discuss priorities and vision to make Toronto a healthier and more v
 ibrant cycling city ahead of the 2026 Municipal Election.\n\nCheck out our
  (/scorecard) Toronto Cycling Council Cycling Scorecard and read (/city_co
 uncil_cycling) our blog post.\n\nMust be a (/join) Cycle Toronto member to
  attend. Not sure if you're a member? Email contribute[at]cycleto[dot]ca t
 o confirm.\nURL: https://www.cycleto.ca/members_town_hall
LOCATION:
URL:https://www.cycleto.ca/members_town_hall
END:VEVENT
