BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Learn\, Plant\, Bike at Yorkview Public School
DTSTART:20260519T200000Z
DTEND:20260519T220000Z
DTSTAMP:20260513T063931Z
UID:9337157b-fa52-5a16-822c-e9d07e44c96b
DESCRIPTION:Yorkview Public School is hosting a community event focused on
  planting\, community and growth. In collaboration with the City of Toront
 o as a part of our StreetSmartsTO initiative\, we are hosting a Bike Engag
 ement Station at Yorkview Public School on Tuesday\, May 19 from 4-6 pm.\n
 \nWe'll be there with some educational materials and will demonstrate how 
 to perform safety checks for those who may not have access to a bike shop 
 but want to get riding. We'll be able to help with things like inflating y
 our tires\, lubricating your chain\, demonstrating how to do an (https://w
 ww.cycleto.ca/abccheck) ABC safety check\, and anything else our teams can
  safely accomplish in a few minutes.\nURL: https://www.cycleto.ca/learn_pl
 ant_bike_at_yorkview_public_school
LOCATION:Yorkview Public School\n130 Yorkview Drive\nNorth York ON M2R 1K1
 \nCA
URL:https://www.cycleto.ca/learn_plant_bike_at_yorkview_public_school
END:VEVENT
