BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Gateway Bike Hub: Giveaway
DTSTART:20260523T150000Z
DTEND:20260523T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260513T063930Z
UID:ba373e17-6b32-52c6-a712-c2b3db30da34
DESCRIPTION:Cycle Toronto will be at Gateway Bikehub's "Project Recycle: B
 ike Giveaway" event on Saturday\, May 23 from 11:00 AM - 1:00 PM. Resident
 s with eligible postal codes can get a FREE bike (1 bike per family\, firs
 t come first served). Come learn more about the different organizations in
  the Thorncliffe Park community!\n\nPlease note that this is a general out
 reach station for Cycle Toronto. No mechanics are offered at this event.\n
 URL: https://www.cycleto.ca/gateway_bike_hub_giveaway
LOCATION:
URL:https://www.cycleto.ca/gateway_bike_hub_giveaway
